snippet.textDisplay:
Thankyou so much Coke Studio for presenting this one.💚 It makes me feel a step closer to my roots and religion, which we are forgetting day by day ❤️I have always heard about this amazing poetry (shikwa/jawab e shikwa) of Sir  Allama Iqbal, but never had the coincidence of reading it.. I have searched many times on internet but couldn’t find it there as well.. Thank you so much for sharing it with our young generation 💓 
Always have heard these line and are one of my favorites,but never knew before that these were from jawab e shikwa... 
 ❤️ کی محمّد سے وفا تو ہم تیرے ہیں  
یہ جہاں چیز ہے کیا لوح و قلم تیرے ہیں 
Looking forward to the whole season 😍 Good luck 👍🏻 Love from Pakistan 🇵🇰 Pakistan Zindabad 💚
